{"tid":708304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"獨攬輸波責任 孫興民向隊友道歉","createTime":"2018-06-19T08:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T12:00:57.000Z","uid":33799,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe6104d84c92d3d99fd4b4b329d6842eb0a7406","tid":708304,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=kfGbL%2FOjNJwp4oeQaGZtP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5f0145dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】韓國於首場世界盃分組賽以0:1不敵瑞典，球隊在整場比賽中未能突破瑞典的防守，5次射門沒1次中目標，賽後，球星孫興民認為自己要負上責任，並向隊友道歉。<br />\n<br />\n「我仍然對我的表現感到十分失望，對隊友感到非常非常抱歉，因為如果我們沒有入球，這是我的錯，我需要承擔責任。」25歲的孫興民（Son Heung-min）在球隊昨日以0:1受挫於瑞典後，簡直想把全隊的輸波責任獨攬上身。 孫興民在國家隊缺乏進攻配合，是役發揮機會不多，甚至不時墮後助守及爭取控球機會，與效力其球會熱刺時，不時與隊友互傳突破，殺到心臟地帶射門明顯有所不同。 <span style=\"color: red;\">孫興民續說，「這當然有點不同，因為當我在熱刺踢球時，每個隊友都是最好的球員之一。而有時候，當我為韓國隊踢球時，我需要傳球給其他球員，這與在熱刺有點不同。」</span><br />\n<br />\n串緊其他都係狗係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5f6cadd924c093dd5e342df4cf3d61af9b132a","tid":708304,"uid":23734,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"爆落底線嗰球<br />\n平時會有HURRY CLAIM接應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23da22eaf4714a18b0d4cb6aa169de9b281748c","tid":708304,"uid":8588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f5f6cadd924c093dd5e342df4cf3d61af9b132a","tid":708304,"uid":23734,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"爆落底線嗰球<br />\n平時會有HURRY CLAIM接應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"就算冇Kane 都有alli後上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl